{"id":"01c9e88e-7e19-4cc4-9f6b-12b66a172ac3","title":"1550/08/16: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"e1bc2e6e-69b3-4a8d-8420-40e9411de984","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, August 16th, 1550.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"2a62903c-76c0-4e26-8bce-413976b0cb95","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"732f013a-11ee-48a0-8262-b8c13a909201","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":27,"value":"a95dd10a-37f3-41b8-8226-54370e72aa0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e5a270c8-949f-42f0-a774-6d391e18dc9f","type":"style/superscript","start":20,"end":21,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"26de4897-b21e-416d-99ba-d501f49f6552","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c2482b34-e078-4fd7-8f45-642a9a1c3351","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"21d084e4-0f9c-4ac4-b4b5-a08f63f2b72b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"8d21859f-2df1-474b-aba5-d3e1e20e9622","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"ebcbd843-194f-42e0-9a33-1b1774096937","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"307d5d8b-966f-49bd-b0f4-93f02f0bf448","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I learn from thy last letter that Cepperello is willing to sell the farm adjoining ours at Settignano which that woman holds for life. If Cepperello wishes to sell it now the price to be paid ought to be based upon a fair assumption of how many years she is likely to live, as the property must necessarily remain hers during her life, passing into\u00A0our hands only at her death. This does not appear to me a very good arrangement because of many things which might happen and which would be full of danger to our interests while we were not in\u00A0possession. Therefore it would be better to wait until she dies. If Cepperello comes to speak to me about it I will tell him what I think, but I shall not\u00A0bother to go to him.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"77be69de-41f7-4954-802f-e1366c68a630","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c279ca9f-679f-4bb0-b3df-effabc0b1f4a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"04ae228e-6e31-4538-99af-63f787d569c5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b3d9cb17-3dbc-4e4d-9705-4e586385774f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":25,"end":27,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"3d04481a-199b-4a74-86bf-ffa7db9ad03e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":46,"end":55,"value":"7560bbfa-96f9-4872-9774-2cdfb0f93924","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"68ac46c6-cb98-4529-9b16-30c62fcd6d01","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":80,"end":83,"value":"f3cc72f0-7f61-4e8d-9743-ab0b6296ff48","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"6548e1f2-8e96-4217-80c0-59a4c7a26f6e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":95,"end":98,"value":"6a06f9ba-3a97-4a7e-a74d-295b866110c7","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b7ddb519-e8b5-4440-a7ee-6e56a12a7b2d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":103,"end":112,"value":"93f44085-a759-46d1-924c-439e1f3a431e","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"132afa76-a3b3-4e3b-9d41-72bbb413fb11","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":125,"end":129,"value":"c7516f50-2421-4160-bd91-8d87478f0732","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"i